## Git attributes for packaging/source exports.
##
## NOTE:
## - `export-ignore` affects `git archive` (zip/tar exports), NOT `git clone/pull`.
## - To prevent files from being tracked on clone/pull, use `.gitignore` and/or
##   remove them from git history (`git rm --cached ...`).

